+## 🔧 API Endpoints
+
+### Real API (via Nuxt Server)
+
+All endpoints are proxied through Nuxt server routes:
+
+| Method | Endpoint                     | Description                       |
+| ------ | ---------------------------- | --------------------------------- |
+| POST   | `/api/hotels/availability`   | Search hotels                     |
+| GET    | `/api/hotels/suggest?query=` | Get destination suggestions       |
+| POST   | `/api/hotels/detail`         | Get hotel details (via checkrate) |
+| POST   | `/api/hotels/checkrate`      | Check rate availability           |
+| POST   | `/api/hotels/booking`        | Create booking                    |
+| DELETE | `/api/hotels/cancel/:ref`    | Cancel booking                    |
+
+### Mock API
+
+Same interface, but uses local data:
+
+```typescript
+import { mockSearchHotels, mockGetSuggestions } from "~/lib/hotels/mockApi";
+
+const results = await mockSearchHotels(params);
+const suggestions = await mockGetSuggestions("Tosh");
+```
+
