+## 🚨 Error Handling
+
+### Automatic Fallback Triggers
+
+The gateway automatically falls back to mock on these errors:
+
+- ✅ Network errors (fetch failed, timeout)
+- ✅ HTTP errors (4xx, 5xx)
+- ✅ CORS errors
+- ✅ Schema validation errors
+- ✅ Server unavailable
+
+### Manual Error Handling
+
+```typescript
+try {
+  const results = await gateway.searchHotels(params);
+} catch (error) {
+  if (error instanceof ApiHttpError) {
+    console.error("API error:", error.status, error.message);
+  } else if (error instanceof ApiParseError) {
+    console.error("Parse error:", error.issues);
+  } else {
+    console.error("Unknown error:", error);
+  }
+}
+```
