+# Hotelbeds API — Triponik to'liq moslashuvi
+
+Barcha mehmonxona logikasi [Hotelbeds dokumentatsiyasi](https://developer.hotelbeds.com/documentation/getting-started/) va **BookingAPI / ContentAPI** Postman kolleksiyalariga **to'liq** mos formatda. Real API va mock **bir xil** so'rov/javob orqali ishlaydi — ulashda farq sezilmaydi.
+
+## Ishlash tartibi (API doc ga mos)
+
+1. **So'rov** — server har doim Hotelbeds formatida yuboradi (`hotelbedsApi.ts`, Postman).
+2. **Javob** — real yoki mock bo'lsin, adapter **bitta** normalized formatga keltiradi.
+3. **Mock** — server fallback ham Hotelbeds **javob** formatida (hotels.hotels[], hotel.checkIn/checkOut, rate.net string va h.k.) beriladi, keyin **o'sha adapter** orqali o'tadi.
+
+## Manbalar
+
+- **Booking API:** `BookingAPI.postman_collection.json` — Availability, CheckRate, Booking
+- **Content API:** `ContentAPI.postman_collection.json` — Hotels, HotelDetails, Locations
+- **Server:** `server/utils/hotelbedsApi.ts` — so'rov/javob turlari (doc ga mos)
+
+## Booking API (format)
+
+| Operatsiya   | Method | Path                         | So'rov (asosiy)                    | Javob (asosiy)              |
+|-------------|--------|------------------------------|------------------------------------|-----------------------------|
+| Availability| POST   | `/hotel-api/1.0/hotels`      | `stay`, `occupancies`, `destination` yoki `hotels.hotel` | `hotels: { hotels: [], checkIn, checkOut, total }`, `currency` |
+| CheckRate   | POST   | `/hotel-api/1.0/checkrates`   | `rooms: [{ rateKey }]`             | `hotel: { checkIn, checkOut, code, rooms[], totalNet, currency }` |
+| Booking     | POST   | `/hotel-api/1.0/bookings`    | booking payload                    | booking reference           |
+
+## Normalized format (adapterlar)
+
+- **Availability:** `adaptAvailabilityResponse(rawPayload, request)` — kirish: Hotelbeds javob (yoki shu formatdagi mock). Chiqish: `checkIn`, `checkOut`, `currency`, `total`, `hotels[]` (har birida `code` string, `rooms[].rates[].rateKey`, `price.net` number).
+- **Detail:** `adaptHotelDetails(rawPayload)` — kirish: CheckRate javob (yoki shu formatdagi mock). Chiqish: `{ hotel: { code, name, rooms, minRate, totalNet, currency, ... }, checkIn, checkOut }`.
+
+## Mock — to'liq mos
+
+- **Availability mock** (`availability.post.ts`): `hotels: { hotels: [...], checkIn, checkOut, total }`, har bir hotel/rate **Postman** dagi kabi (`code` number, `net` string, `boardCode`, `cancellationPolicies`). Keyin `adaptAvailabilityResponse(payload, request)` — real bilan bir xil adapter.
+- **Detail mock** (`detail.post.ts`): CheckRate ko‘rinishida `hotel` (checkIn, checkOut, rooms[].rates[].net string va h.k.) yig‘iladi, keyin `adaptHotelDetails(payload)` — real bilan bir xil adapter.
+- **Client mock** (`mockApi.ts`): `searchHotels` qaytishi allaqachon **normalized** (`HotelSearchResponse` = adapter chiqishi bilan ustma-ust).
+
+## Proxy
+
+Server `getHotelApiBaseUrl()` orqali upstream chaqiradi. Pathlar loyihada `hotel/hotel/availability/`, `hotel/hotel/checkrate/` bo‘lishi mumkin; to‘g‘ridan-to‘g‘ri Hotelbeds uchun `hotelbedsApi.ts` → `BOOKING_API_PATHS`.
+
+## Content API (ixtiyoriy)
+
